:#                     the sub-macro, so that they survive an additional      #
:#                     level of expansion.)                                   #
:#                                                                            #
:#  History                                                                   #
:#   2015-04-15 JFL Initial version, based on dostips.com samples, with       #
:#                  changes so that they work with DelayedExpansion on.       #
